reviewText: with Momiji away Kazuto is in a bad mood and decides to take it out on the rest of the staff. when Momiji finally gets back Kazuto takes her out to a popular fast food restaurant, where he hate the food. after that Kazuto and Momiji head to an arcade for some fun and a picture. when they get home Momiji is punished for have a cold and emotionless look on her face. while being patched up one of the maids tells Momiji that Kazuto may be mean to her, but he was miscible while she was gone and that he needs her. this makes Momiji happy and the next morning her starts her day with a smile.

I absolutely love this series.  A lot of hentai is not a series like this, they are just one disc with 2-3 episodes.  If the first few episodes are good than I am always disappointed that it is over.  But this one is on going.  Can't wait to see more.  She is so fragile and becomes desperate to please her rapist.
